980
01:10:17,350 --> 01:10:19,820
Dear Maggie

981
01:10:19,820 --> 01:10:22,719
Hope you got my email.

982
01:10:22,719 --> 01:10:27,640
And I hope this letter won't make you angry.

983
01:10:27,640 --> 01:10:33,380
I'm coming to England because I must leave
