1030
01:14:08,870 --> 01:14:12,060
But it wasn't easy for the family.

1031
01:14:12,060 --> 01:14:18,560
David wanted Nina to come home and work with
him in the restaurant, but she stayed at the

1032
01:14:18,560 --> 01:14:22,970
