again.

1035
01:14:38,480 --> 01:14:44,820
She never heard from Xavier again either,
and he never arrived in England.

1036
01:14:44,820 --> 01:14:47,980
Maggie was
very sad.

1037
01:14:47,980 --> 01:14:53,199
She really thought that she and Xavier were
great together.

1038
01:14:53,199 --> 01:14:55,520
It was hard for her.

1039
01:14:55,520 --> 01:15:03,820
She wanted to believe that he was a good person,
but all her friends told her to forget him.

1040
01:15:03,820 --> 01:15:07,430
Sometimes she thought about going back to
Chile to find him.

1041
01:15:07,430 --> 01:15:11,340
But in the end, she
didn't.

1042
01:15:11,340 --> 01:15:19,480
She decided that probably it was just a holiday
romance for him after all.

1043
01:15:19,480 --> 01:15:25,170
