the money.

1044
01:15:25,170 --> 01:15:29,690
After a few days, he had another conversation
with his brother.

1045
01:15:29,690 --> 01:15:34,690
Then he decided
to leave his job at the newspaper and write

1046
01:15:34,690 --> 01:15:36,449
a book.

1047
01:15:36,449 --> 01:15:40,900
He worked at home so he could look after Alicia
too.

1048
01:15:40,900 --> 01:15:46,840
At first, it was strange for him, but slowly
he began to enjoy his new life.

1049
01:15:46,840 --> 01:15:53,130
It was exciting to write and Alicia was an
easy child.

1050
01:15:53,130 --> 01:15:55,860
Hannah got a good job in a shop, which
she enjoyed.

1051
01:15:55,860 --> 01:16:04,360
They were still short of money, but one day
about three months later he got a letter from

1052
01:16:04,360 --> 01:16:07,200
Barrett, Grabbe and Lennox.

1053
01:16:07,200 --> 01:16:11,220
Life began to look a lot better for Sam and
his family.

